overview:
KBSD is a Digital Marketing Consultancy headquartered in Geneva, Switzerland.

KBSD is an International Consultancy for Internet Marketing & Interactive Medias Optimization. KBSD is a specialized consultancy in digital marketing dedicated to optimizing internet and interactive medias for companies and prominent individuals, targeting higher return on investment, global branding, online reputation management and conversion rate optimization.

KBSD Mission is stated as Increasing value and exposure for our clients, protecting reputation and implementing strategic solutions to achieve Digital Supremacy.

Products/Services : . Online Brand Protection & Defense . Online Reputation Management (ORM) . International Search Engine Optimization . Audits, Evaluations & Advisory . Analytics, Statistics & Metrics . Social Media Strategies . Internet & Web Expertise . E-Commerce Sales & Conversion Optimization . Online Public Relations & Press Communications . Easter Europe and China SEO
